---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to the CloudSecure Research Blog</h1>
			<p>
				Hi, I'm Alex McCarthy, and I research security automation, red teaming, and AI-driven vulnerability detection on behalf of <strong>CloudSecure</strong>.
			</p>
			<p>
				This blog is a living record of my technical explorations, experiments, and findings. I share insights, prototype designs, and practical guides for building tools that help secure cloud environments and developer workflows.
			</p>
			<h2>Recent Topics</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Automated security scanning and notifications</li>
				<li>Integrating AI models for code analysis</li>
				<li>Red team prototype development</li>
				<li>Prompt engineering and reasoning in LLMs</li>
				<li>Chain of Thought prompting and its impact</li>
				<li>Tree of Thoughts for complex reasoning</li>
				<li>Chain of Preference Optimization</li>
				<li>AI reasoning strategies and model evaluation</li>
				<li>Exploring new cloud security technologies</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Browse the <a href="/blog">blog</a> for daily updates, technical deep-dives, and project progress. If you have questions, feedback, or want to collaborate, please reach out!
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
